---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Contact from "../components/Contact.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Philip Abao, AI researcher and co-founder of Auxerta."
  prose
  colophonLeft="about"
  colophonRight="last updated / 2026/06/12"
>
  <header class="mb-12">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
      <img
        src="/profile.jpg"
        alt="Philip Abao"
        width="120"
        height="120"
        onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/profile.svg'"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
        class="h-24 w-24 flex-none rounded-sm object-cover ring-1 ring-rule-strong"
      />
      <div class="min-w-0 pt-1">
        <h1 class="font-display text-[36px] font-medium leading-none tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-[42px]">
          Philip Abao
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink-3">
          Co-founder, Auxerta / California
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <article>
    <p>
      I'm <strong>Philip Abao</strong>. I'm from the United States, and I've
      lived most of my life in California.
    </p>
    <p>
      I love technology. My uncle introduced me to computer science when I was
      very young, and showed me the good it can do for the world.
    </p>

    <h2>What I work on</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a co-founder of <strong>Auxerta</strong>, where I'm building a
      post-transformer architecture with persistent memory and a new form of
      thought for AI. The goal is models that keep memory and compute flat as
      inputs grow, instead of recomputing everything at each step.
    </p>

    <h2>Now</h2>
    <p>
      Building at Auxerta, and writing here as the work develops.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <Contact variant="stack" />
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
